             was indicted for <rs id="t17940219-28-off152" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17940219-28-off152" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940219-28-off152" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on he <rs id="t17940219-28-cd153" type="crimeDate">15th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940219-28-off152 t17940219-28-cd153"></join>, a quart pewter pot, value 10d. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17940219-28-victim311" type="victimName">
