                  , and a pint pewter pot, value 10d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17940219-28-victim315" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Longworthy
                  <interp inst="t17940219-28-victim315" type="surname" value="Longworthy"></interp>
